          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2">Circular Pitch, p = Pi * m</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-style:normal;">Circular Pitch is the width of a Tooth in mm)</text></para>
